Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 10 of Head MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Pathology' from the dropdown menu
And I select 'I describe' or 'I know' radio button

When I select 'Characterization II' tab
Then 'Displacement' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infiltration' checkbox is enabled

And 'Hydrocephalus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Perifocal edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bony remodeling of the sella region' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dura tail sign' checkbox is enabled
And 'Contact with the internal carotid artery' checkbox is enabled

And 'Displacement of the pituitary stalk' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infiltration into the cavernous sinus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Extension to suprasellar' checkbox is enabled

And 'No' radio button is disabled
And 'Weak' radio button is disabled
And 'Significant' radio button is disabled
And 'Detection of the lesion after contrast agent administration' checkbox is disabled


When I select 'Displacement' checkbox
And I select 'Infiltration' checkbox
Then 'Displacement' checkbox is selected
And 'Infiltration' checkbox is selected

When I select 'Hydrocephalus' checkbox
And I select 'Perifocal edema' checkbox
And I select 'Bony remodeling of the sella region' checkbox
And I select 'Dura tail sign' checkbox
Then 'Hydrocephalus' checkbox is selected
And 'Perifocal edema' checkbox is selected
And 'Bony remodeling of the sella region' checkbox is selected
And 'Dura tail sign' checkbox is selected

When I select 'Contact with the internal carotid artery' checkbox
Then 'Contact with the internal carotid artery' checkbox is selected
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Right' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is selected
When I select 'Left' radio button
Then 'Left' radio button is selected

When I select 'Displacement of the pituitary stalk' checkbox
Then 'Displacement of the pituitary stalk' checkbox is selected
And 'To the right' radio button is enabled
And 'To the left' radio button is enabled
When I select 'To the right' radio button
Then 'To the right' radio button is selected
When I select 'To the left' radio button
Then 'To the left' radio button is selected

When I select 'Infiltration into the cavernous sinus' checkbox
Then 'Infiltration into the cavernous sinus' checkbox is selected
And 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Suspicion of' checkbox
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is selected

When I select 'Extension to suprasellar' checkbox
Then 'Extension to suprasellar' checkbox is selected
And 'Affection optic chiasm' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Affection optic chiasm' checkbox
Then 'Affection optic chiasm' checkbox is selected
